      <xref linkend="python"/>,
      <ulink url="http://www.xmms.org/">XMMS</ulink>,
      <xref linkend="graphviz"/>, and
      <xref linkend="doxygen"/>
    </para>

    <para condition="html" role="usernotes">Notes utilisateur&nbsp;:
